<h2><a href="http://www.rationalargumentator.com/index/blog/2014/07/victory-truth/" title="Permanent Link to The Victory of Truth is Never Assured! (2009) &#8211; Article by G. Stolyarov II" rel="bookmark">The Victory of Truth is Never Assured! (2009) &#8211; Article by G. Stolyarov II</a></h2>
<p><a href="http://www.rationalargumentator.com/index/blog/2014/07/victory-truth/#respond" class="comments-link"  title="Comment on The Victory of Truth is Never Assured! (2009) &#8211; Article by G. Stolyarov II">No comments yet</a></p>	
